desc: Stymie Clothing Company offers casual golf and non-golf themed apparel for everyday use. From comfortable t-shirts to stylish hats, Stymie Clothing Co. has you covered for your lifestyle "off the course."

layout.text: You can take a kid from Hawaii, but you'll never take Hawaii out of a kid! We've tapped into our island roots and came up with a couple of designs to represent where we came from.
